{"word":"G3551 - νόμος - nómos - nom'-os - Law","slug":"G3551","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">νόμος</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>nómos"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>nom'-os"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Law"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x03BD;&#x03BF;&#x0301;&#x03BC;&#x03BF;&#x03C2; - nomos</b> - <i>nom'-os</i><p/>From a primary word <b>&#x03BD;&#x03B5;&#x0301;&#x03BC;&#x03C9;</b> <b>nemo&#x0304;</b> (to <i>parcel</i> out, especially <i>food</i> or <i>grazing</i> to animals); <i>law</i> (through the idea of prescriptive <i>usage</i>), generally (<i>regulation</i>), specifically (of Moses [including the volume]; also of the Gospel), or figuratively (a <i>principle</i>): - law."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/G1772\">G1772</a>, <a href=\"#/G3544\">G3544</a>, <a href=\"#/G3545\">G3545</a>, <a href=\"#/G3547\">G3547</a>, <a href=\"#/G3548\">G3548</a>, <a href=\"#/G3549\">G3549</a>, <a href=\"#/G3550\">G3550</a>, <a href=\"#/G3891\">G3891</a>, <a href=\"#/G3892\">G3892</a>, <a href=\"#/G458\">G458</a>, <a href=\"#/G459\">G459</a>, <a href=\"#/G460\">G460</a>"}]}